ğŸ§  MOST IMPORTANT INTERVIEW FORMULAS â­
n & 1                  # odd / even
n & (n - 1)            # remove rightmost set bit
n & -n                 # get rightmost set bit
n | (n + 1)            # set rightmost unset bit
n & (n - 1) == 0       # power of 2

